0.5.8  2022-06-07T16:19:57+12:00
   - Use PDF::Grammar v0.2.9+ :lite mode for lighter AST's.
   - Numeric objects are no longer cast to roles PDF::COS::Int,
     PDF::COS::Bool, PDF::COS::Real unless they are indirect
     objects.
